In 2 weeks I will be 34.
I am so damn proud of the woman I am today. I am becoming the woman I’ve always wanted to be. I can truly say I LOVE MYSELF. I love my shadows, they are the doorways to my healing and they give me the contrast which creates my uniqueness. I love my light, it’s not actually mine but all of ours. We light ourselves up and then light each other up, and soon the world will be once again on fire with love. I have spent most of my life here on earth searching for deeper wisdom, and I understand it all lies within. I was put here on this earth to teach you how to love yourself. We are all worthy and welcome.. or else we wouldn’t be here, I can promise you that! Next time you look at yourself in the mirror, please take a deep look into your eyes and give yourself a smile ✨💕🙏🏽
